---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const seo = {"title": "Threads — Smooth Threads | D‑Essence Wellness", "description": "Subtle collagen‑stimulating threads to refine and firm skin.", "canonical": "/services/smooth-threads", "type": "website", "ogImage": "/og-default" };
---

<BaseLayout {...seo}>

<section class="relative isolate bg-neutral-950 text-white pt-28 md:pt-32">
  <!-- HERO Minimal -->
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6">
    <nav class="text-sm text-white/60 mb-2">
      <a href="/" class="hover:text-white/90">Home</a>
      <span class="mx-1">/</span>
      <a href="/services" class="hover:text-white/90">Services</a>
      <span class="mx-1">/</span>
      <span class="text-white/90">Threads — Smooth Threads</span>
    </nav>
    <div class="py-6">
      <h1 class="text-[2.25rem] md:text-5xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Threads — Smooth Threads</h1>
      <p class="mt-3 text-white/80 text-lg max-w-3xl">Subtle collagen‑stimulating threads to refine and firm skin.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="h-px w-full bg-white/10"></div>
  </div>

  <!-- Horizontal TOC chips -->
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6">
    <div class="flex gap-2 py-4 overflow-x-auto no-scrollbar">
      <a href="#overview" class="shrink-0 rounded-full border border-white/10 px-3 py-1 text-white/80 hover:text-white hover:bg-white/5">Overview</a>
      <a href="#indications" class="shrink-0 rounded-full border border-white/10 px-3 py-1 text-white/80 hover:text-white hover:bg-white/5">Indications</a>
      <a href="#candidates" class="shrink-0 rounded-full border border-white/10 px-3 py-1 text-white/80 hover:text-white hover:bg-white/5">Who it's for</a>
      <a href="#process" class="shrink-0 rounded-full border border-white/10 px-3 py-1 text-white/80 hover:text-white hover:bg-white/5">What to Expect</a>
      <a href="#timeline" class="shrink-0 rounded-full border border-white/10 px-3 py-1 text-white/80 hover:text-white hover:bg-white/5">Timeline</a>
      <a href="#aftercare" class="shrink-0 rounded-full border border-white/10 px-3 py-1 text-white/80 hover:text-white hover:bg-white/5">Aftercare</a>
      <a href="#faqs" class="shrink-0 rounded-full border border-white/10 px-3 py-1 text-white/80 hover:text-white hover:bg-white/5">FAQs</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Two-Column Main -->
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 pb-24 grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-10">
    <!-- Main Narrative -->
    <article class="lg:col-span-8 space-y-8">
      <section id="overview" class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-neutral-900 p-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold">Overview</h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-white/80">
          This service focuses on natural‑looking improvement while prioritizing comfort, safety, and education.
          We co‑create a plan around your goals, explain each step, and share what to expect before and after treatment.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section id="indications" class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-neutral-900 p-6">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">Indications</h3>
        <ul class="mt-3 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-3 text-white/80 list-disc pl-5">
          <li>Concerns and areas vary by service and anatomy.</li>
          <li>We aim for balance, proportion, and a refined finish.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section id="candidates" class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-neutral-900 p-6">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">Who It’s For</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-white/80">Healthy individuals with specific concerns and realistic expectations. Certain conditions, medications, or allergies may require modifications or make a service unsuitable. Always review your medical history with your provider.</p>
      </section>

      <section id="process" class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-neutral-900 p-6">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">What to Expect</h3>
        <ol class="mt-3 list-decimal pl-5 space-y-2 text-white/80">
          <li>Consultation & goal setting</li>
          <li>Customized technique/product or device selection</li>
          <li>Treatment and aftercare guidance</li>
        </ol>
      </section>

      <section id="timeline" class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-neutral-900 p-6">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">Timeline</h3>
        <div class="mt-3 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-3 text-white/80">
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-neutral-800 p-4"><p class="text-white/70 text-sm">Visit length</p><p class="text-white font-medium mt-1">~30–60 minutes</p></div>
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-neutral-800 p-4"><p class="text-white/70 text-sm">Downtime</p><p class="text-white font-medium mt-1">Minimal for most</p></div>
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-neutral-800 p-4"><p class="text-white/70 text-sm">Maintenance</p><p class="text-white font-medium mt-1">Personalized plan</p></div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="aftercare" class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-neutral-900 p-6">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">Aftercare</h3>
        <ul class="mt-3 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-3 text-white/80 list-disc pl-5">
          <li>Follow your personalized post‑care handout.</li>
          <li>Protect the area and avoid irritants as directed.</li>
          <li>Hydrate, rest, and use only recommended products.</li>
          <li>Report unexpected reactions promptly.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section id="faqs" class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-neutral-900 p-6">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">FAQs</h3>
        <div class="mt-3 space-y-4 text-white/80">
          <details class="group rounded-lg border border-white/10 p-4">
            <summary class="font-medium text-white cursor-pointer">How many sessions will I need?</summary>
            <p class="mt-2">It varies by concern and modality. Your provider will outline a personalized plan and maintenance if appropriate.</p>
          </details>
          <details class="group rounded-lg border border-white/10 p-4">
            <summary class="font-medium text-white cursor-pointer">Will it look natural?</summary>
            <p class="mt-2">Our approach focuses on subtle, harmonious changes that complement your features.</p>
          </details>
          <details class="group rounded-lg border border-white/10 p-4">
            <summary class="font-medium text-white cursor-pointer">Is there downtime?</summary>
            <p class="mt-2">Most services have minimal downtime. Temporary redness, swelling, or sensitivity can occur and usually resolves quickly.</p>
          </details>
        </div>
      </section>

      <p class="text-white/60 text-sm">*Informational content only; not medical advice. Individual results vary.</p>
    </article>

    <!-- Side Notes / Secondary -->
    <aside class="lg:col-span-4 space-y-6">
      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-neutral-900 p-6">
        <h4 class="text-base font-semibold">At a Glance</h4>
        <dl class="mt-3 grid grid-cols-1 gap-2 text-white/80">
          <div class="flex justify-between"><dt class="text-white/70">Session length</dt><dd>~30–60 minutes</dd></div>
          <div class="flex justify-between"><dt class="text-white/70">Downtime</dt><dd>Minimal</dd></div>
          <div class="flex justify-between"><dt class="text-white/70">Discomfort</dt><dd>Mild to moderate</dd></div>
          <div class="flex justify-between"><dt class="text-white/70">Maintenance</dt><dd>Personalized</dd></div>
        </dl>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-neutral-900 p-6">
        <h4 class="text-base font-semibold">Good to Know</h4>
        <ul class="mt-2 space-y-2 text-white/80 list-disc pl-5">
          <li>Tailored protocols and premium products/devices</li>
          <li>Comfort‑forward techniques</li>
          <li>Clear guidance and realistic timelines</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </aside>
  </div>
</section>

</BaseLayout>
